description:
Possibly the best trash talker U/S has to offer, Penner Barber, shows off why she's so cocky with a completely dominant match against the rookie, Tina "professor Booty" Horne. The professor sure puts up some effort but it's pathetic effort. It's so pathetic, actually, that Princess Donna gives out her first and ONLY "Shame" points to date.
This is a welterweight match up but it's a squash match. The winner doles out a outrageous spanking to the loser with 100 spanks. While making the losers tushy bright read, the Winner has an orgasm over her face then fucks her like a true champions while verbally belittling her wrestling skills.
title: Penny " The Tarrasque" Barber vs Tina "professor Booty" Horne
